  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为FinTech交易队列设计一个完整的故障注入测试流程。核心场景是：从本地机器发起，经过ESP32控制器，最终到达目标子系统。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Local Machine",
        "ESP32 Controller",
        "Target Subsystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我理解为这是一个硬件在环的故障测试架构？ESP32作为中间控制器，通过SPI与目标子系统通信？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ESP32 Controller",
        "Target Subsystem",
        "SPI Fault Frame"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对。第一步是本地机器向ESP32下发\"Design Fault Injection Campaign\"指令，然后ESP32构造SPI故障帧，这里要标注为FinTech_PaymentGateway类型。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Local Machine",
        "ESP32 Controller",
        "SPI Fault Frame",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把这条主链路画出来：GS到ESP的设计指令，然后ESP到TS的SPI故障帧。接下来目标子系统怎么处理这个帧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Local Machine",
        "ESP32 Controller",
        "Target Subsystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "目标子系统收到后，把帧转给FaultManager。FaultManager需要先验证状态掩码，然后配置故障参数。这是关键的两步内部处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Target Subsystem",
        "FaultManager",
        "Validate State Mask",
        "Configure Fault Parameters"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：TS到FM的Process SPI Frame，以及FM内部的两步处理。我注意到这里有个状态需要标注——正常操作期间的状态，用FinTech_AuthVault色块包围？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FaultManager",
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "Normal Operation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，那个色块标注\"Normal Operation Continues\"，覆盖TS和FM。然后FM要向LedgerService发送消息，同时查询TransactionQueue的故障是否激活。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FaultManager",
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "isFaultActive"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这里进入分支判断了。我看到三种情况：TransactionQueue故障、LedgerService故障、以及TransactionQueue无故障。用alt结构？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "alt"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，第一个分支是TransactionQueue故障激活的情况。这时候TransportDecorator要介入，应用故障到LedgerService上。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TransportDecorator",
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "Apply Fault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画了第一个alt分支：FM询问TD是否激活，TD内部标注Active+Parameters，然后TD应用故障。返回应该是TIMEOUT或CRC_ERROR？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FaultManager",
        "TransportDecorator",
        "TIMEOUT",
        "CRC_ERROR"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，虚线返回表示异常响应。第二个分支是LedgerService故障的情况，这时候要走Platform HAL进行硬件层注入。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "Platform HAL",
        "Hardware Manipulation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "理解。所以第二个分支里，FM把Active+Parameters发给HAL，HAL执行injectFault到TransactionQueue，然后进行Hardware Manipulation？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FaultManager",
        "Platform HAL",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "injectFault",
