      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我检查一下：第一个分支的色块是FinTech_AuthVault标注Active+Parameters，第二个分支也是FinTech_AuthVault，第三个是FinTech_FraudDetection。这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
